\begin_layout Plain Layout
Bodey B, Bodey B Jr, Kaiser HE: Apoptosis in the mammalian thymus during
 normal histogenesis and under various in vitro and in vivo experimental
 conditions.
 In Vivo 1998;12:123-133
\end_layout

\end_deeper
