reviews have described essential roles of PCD as a mechanism for quantitative
 matching, sculpting, and deleting anatomical structures, regulating cell
 number, and eliminating error-prone or defective cells (Buss et al., 2006;
 Fuchs and Steller, 2011; Yeo and Gautier, 2004).
